asis is a skin condition that can run in families, so that's definitely something to consider.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.042454,0.078153,0.08914,0.096097,0.099259,0.1015,0.10157,0.09623,0.095779,0.091104,0.069733,0.038985],"unified_progress":[0.044322,0.073472,0.091423,0.096289,0.1024,0.10371,0.10025,0.09439,0.088558,0.082134,0.069808,0.053243]},{"section":10,"text":"But wait, psoriasis usually doesn't show up in babies this young, does it?","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.042112,0.052244,0.064386,0.07514,0.08573,0.096834,0.10673,0.11409,0.11943,0.11702,0.085045,0.04124],"unified_progress":[0.046359,0.064418,0.07823,0.087126,0.095287,0.099388,0.099947,0.10093,0.096455,0.097383,0.078556,0.055925]},{"section":11,"text":"It's more common in adults or older kids.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038551,0.048121,0.058897,0.069884,0.080834,0.093367,0.10501,0.11385,0.12119,0.12161,0.094766,0.053908],"unified_progress":[0.043247,0.060996,0.075511,0.083924,0.092293,0.097507,0.098607,0.10124,0.098506,0.098962,0.084304,0.064904]},{"section":12,"text":"So, maybe not psoriasis itself, but something similar could be going on.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.021317,0.038646,0.054928,0.068413,0.079878,0.094033,0.10719,0.12044,0.12874,0.1273,0.1004,0.058715],"unified_progress":[0.031539,0.055037,0.07056,0.080822,0.090282,0.093313,0.098629,0.10383,0.10363,0.10909,0.093103,0.070162]},{"section":13,"text":"Let's see, the rash is described as having greasy yellow scales.","dimension":5,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.024832,0.050825,0.070967,0.085713,0.094125,0.10015,0.10275,0.10536,0.10694,0.11017,0.092543,0.055634],"unified_progress":[0.036524,0.064429,0.076304,0.089205,0.092258,0.095143,0.10285,0.097909,0.096619,0.098827,0.085309,0.064622]},{"section":14,"text":"That's a big clue!","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate"